As a VIP user, you may use these commands in the hub:

+rules                   -- Display a list of hub rules.
+faq                     -- Display a list of helpful links if you are having trouble.
+motd                    -- Display the Message of the Day.
+help                    -- Display this help message.
+regme                   -- Send a message to all OPs asking them to register your nick.
+myip                    -- Show you your IP address.
+myinfo                  -- Show you information about yourself.
+me                      -- Replace +me with your nick and then send a message to main chat.
+report <user> <reason>  -- Report a user to opchat for breaking the rules.
